sellerCard.description:
My name is Qasim. I consider myself a passionate software engineer who is always willing to learn and explore new technologies and then apply it in real world scenarios.

I have more than 17 years of experience spent in developing/designing and managing different software solutions for Hospitality/Publishing industry, online banking, process automation, real estate and e-commerce sectors. I have a comprehensive experience in web applications/site design and development in Dot Net using C #. I have an extensive experience of Java scripting, Angular, Jquery, Html, Restful API, PHP, Wordpress.

description.content:
I am an experienced web developer having more than 12 years of industry experience.

I am an expert in web application security especially web api security.

I provide Management Consultancy Services free with the project.

Please discuss with me before placing order.

Why me?

  • I deliver quality in time
  • Free Revisions
  • I can handle big and long term projects
  • Reasonable Prices and more reasonable for regular customer.
  • Quick Response times and Good Communication


Full-stack development

  • HTML
  • CSS
  • Bootstrap
  • JavaScript
  • Laravel
  • Angular
  • React
  • NodeJs


From Building a solution from Ground up to Doing Specific Tasks , I can :

  • -Install and Setup any Ecommerce Solution on Your Hosting.
  • -Setup WordPress, Joomla, Magento, Drupal Applications according to requirements.
  • -Install and customize any theme to your liking.
  • -Provide completely Responsive layouts.
  • -Setting up of Payment Gateways on your store.
  • -Develop custom and Laravel, CodeIgniter php solutions/ webapps
  • -Domain migrations, Domain Setups, Security Integrations, API setups, Mobile Apps and Much More.

reviews.comment:
Meraki IT has been a diamond in the rough for us as far as experiences working with freelancers on web development projects.  We have been very much pleasantly surprised with their flexibility to things we've realized needed adjusting along the way, without these projects turning into giant "more money, more money" affairs.  They are very fair and above the table with everything, which we appreciate very much.

If you are looking for someone to partner with you and bring a concept to life, look no further.
Although in the initial stages, he is very knowledgeable in what is required for the project and provided honest opinion of what can be done to improve current system.
Amazing work! We would absolutely work with Qasim again.

We are working with Qasim and team on an an active web platform project.  They have been completely professional, transparent, and proactive with communication each step of the way.  This gig was for outlining, designing, and building a clickable outline site so there is no confusion of what is expected with each page/feature.  We are confident moving forward to the next phase of our project with this development team.
